Subtitle
textBox.plain: This concludes our Module. Please take the time to complete the Module Feedback. Once you have completed the Module Feedback, we recommend that you go to the Supplementary Materials to review the additional information. A Module Test is available for you to take in order to check your understanding of the material or practice for the Certification Exam. The required pass rate for all Module Tests is 80%. You may take this test as many times as you wish: please allow 24 hours between each attempt. Once you have passed all the Module Tests with at least 80% you will be invited to take the Certification Exam.
